verbose_text: The DCF fluorescence intensity was significantly higher in the LPS / PepG, LPS / PepG + ncRNA and LPS / PepG + siRNA groups than that in the control group (2.50 +/-0.10, 2.49 +/-0.08, 3.28 +/-0.17, respectively vs. 1.00 +/-0.12, F = 183.8, P < 0.05, n = 3; XREF_FIG), indicating an enhanced production of ROS stimulated by LPS / PepG.
